description: Letter dated 19/08/2009 from Shahid Malik MP to Andrew Dismore MP regarding inaccuracies in the estimated figures detailing how many people were rescued by the Fire and Rescue Service from (a) all fires and (b) dwellings fires in each (i) fire authority area and (ii) region in each of the last three years. 1 p.
department: Dept for Communities and Local Government
